            "physical_description": "Circular micromosaic tabletop depicting a central group of four genii floating in the open sky, bearing the attributes of painting, music, architecture and sculpture. Around the circumference are eight views of Italian cities: Piazza del Duomo, Milan; St. Mark's Square, Venice; Piazza della Signoria, Florence; St. Peter's Square, Rome; the Colosseum, Rome; the Riviera di Chaia, Naples; St. Rosalia, Palermo and the Harbour at Genoa. The table base is gilt bronze and consists of four legs surmounted with rams heads.", 
